@AcsConversationApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:7195

### Variables
@customerId = 101

### Get all customers
GET {{AcsConversationApi_HostAddress}}/customers
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all support tickets
GET {{AcsConversationApi_HostAddress}}/tickets
Accept: application/json

###

### Get support tickets for specific customer
GET {{AcsConversationApi_HostAddress}}/tickets?customerId={{customerId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Send SMS to customer
POST {{AcsConversationApi_HostAddress}}/sms/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "message": "Hello! This is a test SMS message from customer service."
}

###

### Process inbound SMS (webhook simulation)
POST {{AcsConversationApi_HostAddress}}/sms/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "from": "+14075551111",
    "to": "+18882861538",
    "message": "Thank you for your help!",
    "messageId": "test-message-id-123"
  }
}

###

### Send email to customer
POST {{AcsConversationApi_HostAddress}}/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "subject": "Support Update",
  "body": "Hello Andrew! We have an update regarding your support ticket. Please let us know if you have any questions."
}

###

### Process inbound email (webhook simulation)
POST {{AcsConversationApi_HostAddress}}/email/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "imran+1@example.com",
  "to": "admin+9901@pl26.onmicrosoft.com",
  "bodyPreview": "Thank you for the quick response. I have no further questions.",
  "receivedDateTime": "2024-10-14T15:30:00Z",
  "conversationId": "email-conversation-456"
}